Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:21.36,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I... to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.12,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...might love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Vallière {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Vallière {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:40.10,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.10,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Spy's Seal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it exists... it exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eléonore-oneesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you up early?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's convenient for me. Pack up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on, Eléonore-oneesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you be my personal maid until we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.51,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rowdy people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little tight in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes, closing in on her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-Louise! I'm not done talking yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep looking away, too. Settle down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my familiar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, this military training and whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Academy has degraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you in a place like that any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back home and commit to bridal training instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes", you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Chibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem well these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have... realised Saito-san's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have chosen Miss Vallière...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That perverted dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Louise's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Eléonore-sama and Louise-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, little Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a hot one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Chii-neesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, let me have a good look of your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you've become beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cattleya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I'm hungry, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Tell Louise for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should stay home from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's an outcast at school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not the same as I used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping out Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says that she needs my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could you possibly do when you have zero talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, let's get a groom for Louise already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the second-born son of the Albert family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Groom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it turn out that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about marriage, shouldn't {\i1}you{\i0} get married first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your engagement with Count Burgundy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, that topic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chibi-Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To talk back to me with sarcasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks like you attitude has grown bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The engagement has been dissolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been dissolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Something like "I can't take it anymore".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eléonore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having dinner right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall speak of Louise when Father comes home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Louise really is a lady from a rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her world is different from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides... besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they serious about getting her a groom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Saito-san loves Miss Vallière,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of giving up on him and stepping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they don't seem to have made any progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a woman, I'm in an equal position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm clearly better than her in some categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Eléonore-oneesama always mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always bullies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're cute, she's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she loves you, she can't stop pestering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you, I can understand everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at an age of falling in love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really, I'm not in love with anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san. Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't get to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking of someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that boy you brought with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't love him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I never asked if you loved him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama, I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, she hates me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not... because I want to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural to keep your familiar around you at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to him since I bet he's worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not having his master around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's really all there is to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in Saito's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my familiar's bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he told me... to come to his room tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came because Saito-san asked me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise's room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the groom thing you guys were talking about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret having dissolved our engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't say anything and make love to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, at your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did she have this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a plebeian doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I went into the wrong room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plebeians without manners must be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come close to you ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to, even if asked to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My tongue slipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Louise returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late in returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the military meeting run overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I must soon leave again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Military life really is pathetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dispatching troops and inflaming the citizens with war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a problematic Queen we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Father! Queen Henrietta isn't aggravating the war at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you possibly understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Louise. You do not have to force yourself to learn magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return home and get yourself a groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the end of this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should quickly arrange Louise's engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best way to get her settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? If you're talking about marriage, shouldn't {\i1}you{\i0} get married first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that my engagement got dissolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not ready to get married yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, Nee-sama, you're troubling Louise with this sudden marriage talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise. Is there someone you're currently in a relationship with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, I don't! There's no such person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like you {\i1}do{\i0} have someone on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which aristocrat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A count? Or a baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's a baronet or something even lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fallen in love with someone of a lower status?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl keeps worrying me no matter how old she gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in love with anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Louise is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I please come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks mature, kind and so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Louise will look like this when she grows up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise will grow to be more attractive than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, at this rate, Louise will have to get a groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't want that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in the courtyard, so go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she was little, she would hide in the boat in the courtyard any time something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find Louise, go outside of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A horse carriage is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May primogenitor's blessings be upon both you and Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.43,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Primogenitor: One's earliest male ancestor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of my cute little sister, Knight-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knight... You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in love with anyone, since Saito likes the maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes her more than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister prepared a carriage for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. I don't care about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I can't tell my family... about my Void magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody gives me credit, no matter how much I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you credit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assent to everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stand up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me... when you were the one who called the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would willingly please a selfish girl like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would willingly be a familiar for a flat-chested master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll say it as many times as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about all this war, mission and groom stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at your face makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what being in love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you blab about maids and whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I risk my life by fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um... um... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since you've sworn your loyalty to me by saying that you love your master,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess you do deserve a reward...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just one spot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can touch anywhere you want on your master's body, just one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't rush like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so full of yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decapitate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so close, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. We can talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're handsome guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about Louise, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can trust what you said earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you called her to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your older sister was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You touched Eléonore-oneesama, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I had no intention of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister was the one who jumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you {\i1}did{\i0} sneak into her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I mistook her room for yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a fool for believing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can make Saito-san happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:47.92,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable. I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my womanly charm, I'll beat Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.62,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you investigating so stealthily?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister would never steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spy's Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
